## Development

### Creating a New Component

1. Create folder: `foundation/src/components/MyComponent/`

2. Add `index.jsx`:
   ```jsx
   import { H1, P, cn } from '@uniweb/kit'

   export function MyComponent({ content, params }) {
     const { title } = content.main?.header || {}
     const { theme = 'light' } = params || {}

     return (
       <section className={cn('py-20', theme === 'dark' && 'bg-gray-900')}>
         <H1 text={title} />
       </section>
     )
   }

   export default MyComponent
   ```

3. Add `meta.js`:
   ```javascript
   export default {
     title: 'My Component',
     description: 'Description of what it does',
     category: 'Content',

     elements: {
       title: { label: 'Title', required: true },
       paragraphs: { label: 'Description' },
     },

     properties: {
       theme: {
         type: 'select',
         label: 'Theme',
         options: [
           { value: 'light', label: 'Light' },
           { value: 'dark', label: 'Dark' },
         ],
         default: 'light',
       },
     },
   }
   ```

4. Rebuild: `cd foundation && pnpm build`

